        "client_msg_id": "c758c520-a187-4e11-8a66-41e7cd225fa7",
        "text": "Both of these have been hollowed out by software size and complexity since then. Legally, I am allowed to modify Firefox as I like. Technically, I can't even compile it from source code any more. And with bugs that span layers of dependencies, cognitively limited eyeballs are no longer sufficient, no matter their number.",
